<p>they obtained a sweeping victory over the 6th Batt however.  On that occasion I helped serve out the tea biscuits &amp; eatables to the Lancashire band &amp; the cricketers.</p>
<p>I have been practising bowling a fair bit &amp; improving the batting, but our team is far too good for any immediate chance of my playing.</p>
